thread.title: Rebecca Keegan

author: Rebecca Keegan
title: Rebecca Keegan
text: Very good service and system for first time insurance. Once you buy enough kms and don't speed there are no problems. The weekly text is a great motivator. I would not reccomend staying with boxymo with full licence and driving on motorway as it is not always possible to slow down to speed limit on time when exiting motorway because of heavy traffic behind which then reflects badly on monthly driving score.
